<p>Boat tours are lead by local cooperative, Padre Ramos Tours, and Ibis Kayaking. Padre Ramos Tours consists of seven local guides who are all fantastic resources for the local flora and fauna of the area. Several tour options exist including winding through the mangroves to heading out to the Gulf of Fonseca. The tours are available in Spanish only.</p>

<h2>Horse back riding</h2>

<p>Horse rentals are available, giving you freedom to explore the beach and nearby communities at your leisure. Horses can be rented by the hour with or without a Spanish speaking guide.</p>

<h2>Spanish lessons</h2>

<p>Azael Pineda, our former night-watchman who has been successful in raising literacy rates within his community of Padre Ramos, independently offers Spanish lessons for $5 per hour per person.  Maximum of three students.</p>

